From Rob Steele Subject Re Accepting Jeesus in your heart In article A Eric Molas writes We are just animals We need sleep, food, and we reproduce And we die I agree we need sleep etc, but I disagree we are just animals That statement is a categorical negative it's like saying there are no polkadoted elephants It may be true but one would have to be omniscient to know for sure Rob Steele In coming to understand anything MIT Lincoln Laboratory we are rejecting the facts as they Wood St , M are for us in favour of the facts Lexington, MA as they are C S Lewis